                                        Type: TaylorSeries(Fraction(Integer))
(2) -&gt; sin(x+y)

                     1  3   1    2   1  2    1  3
   (2)  (Y + X) + (- - Y  - - X Y  - - X Y - - X ) + O(5)
                     6      2        2       6
                                        Type: TaylorSeries(Fraction(Integer))

